			March 28, 2013 at 9:12 pm</a>		</div>

		<p>@Ronron</p>
<p><a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YHMYkUrV7A" rel="nofollow">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-YHMYkUrV7A</a></p>
<p>Or like René Descartes would say &#8221;Je pense donc je suis.&#8221; <img src="http://47mb5740sj2k1xsfst40mqbb16bh.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" />  To be or not to be, that is the question. <img src="http://47mb5740sj2k1xsfst40mqbb16bh.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>

