			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e2201c47c4262f2afe91fe8e03fa9931?s=60&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D60&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-60 photo' height='60' width='60' />			<cite class="fn">aleksy</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
